(283,	7,	'LECON ALGEBRE PARTIE37777777',	'<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm;\r\nbackground:#FFF2CC;mso-background-themecolor:accent4;mso-background-themetint:\r\n51\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">MARKETING<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">DEFINITION </span></i></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">:\r\nEnsemble des actions destinées a détectées les besoins et à adapter en\r\nconséquence et de façon continue la production et la commercialisation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"452\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:169.65pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">SELON\r\n  PHILIP KOTLER<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"448\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:168.05pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">SELON MERCATOR<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"375\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:140.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">SELON AAM<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"452\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:169.65pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">Ensemble\r\n  des actions </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\r\n  mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n  mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:\r\n  Wingdings\">à</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"> prévoir,\r\n  susciter les besoins du consommateur d’une catégorie bien ciblé de produit ou\r\n  service.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"448\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:168.05pt;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">Le\r\n  marketing est l’effort d’adaptation des organisations à des marchés\r\n  concurrentiels<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"375\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:140.8pt;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">Le\r\n  marketing est une fonction de l’organisation et un ensemble de processus\r\n  visant à créer, communiquer et délivrer de la valeur aux clients