ast\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:14.2pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:698.3pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"1013\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 379.9pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 698.3pt;\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">II.\r\n  Le Centre De Service Informatique<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Référencé\r\n  Avec ITIL <span style=\"color:red\">p9</span><o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Définition<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\">Le premier point de contact entre les utilisateurs et une\r\n  organisation IT. <b><u>Selon ITIL,</u></b> le centre de services est le point\r\n  de contact unique (SPOC : Single Point of Contact) entre le prestataire de\r\n  services (IT) et les utilisateurs pour les activités quotidiennes. Un centre\r\n  classique gère les incidents et les demandes des services mais a traitant les\r\n  communications des utilisateurs concernant les pannes ou les modifications\r\n  dans le service. <span style=\"color:#C45911;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\n  mso-themeshade:191\">Il couvre un large éventail et est pour fournir à\r\n  l\'utilisateur un guichet unique pour tous leurs besoins informatiques. Ainsi,\r\n  le centre de services joue <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\">Rôle&nbsp;: Faciliter l\'intégration des processus <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">business</span> avec <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">l\'écosystème technologique</span>\r\n  et <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">l\'infrastructure\r\n  élargie de la gestion de services</span>.<span style=\"color:#C45911;\r\n  mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;Origine et évolution dans la Gestion des\r\n  Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La fonction du <span style=\"color:red\">support client</span> est née à la fin des années 80 afin\r\n  d’aider à régler les problèmes. Ils ne possédaient pas de SLA, ni d’objectifs\r\n  basés sur le temps pour régler les problèmes. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ITIL est apparu\r\n  dans les années 90, recensant les meilleures pratiques de la gestion des\r\n  services informatiques, que le concept du centre de services informatiques\r\n  centré sur l\'utilisateur a commencé à émerger. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Centre\r\n  de Service informatique : Support Client et Centre d’Appel<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\">Le Support\r\n  client&nbsp;:</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#385623;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:128\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Est une ressource conçue pour\r\n  fournir au client ou à l\'utilisateur interne des renseignements et du support\r\n  associés aux processus, produits et services de l\'entreprise.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Canaux&nbsp;:\r\n  Site physique, web, messagerie instantanées ou mail….<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\">Le centre\r\n  d’appel&nbsp;: </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Un\r\n  centre d\'appels ou un centre de contacts est un point central qui gère les\r\n  contacts et les <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Interactions\r\n  clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\r\n  color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\">è<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#538135;mso-themecolor:\r\n  accent6;mso-themeshade:191\">Centre d\'appels</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:red\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\">entrants</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;