nt les outils dont ils ont besoin pour réussir<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n  </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  background:fuchsia;mso-highlight:fuchsia\">Utiliser la technologie pour aider\r\n  le centre de services informatiques</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Etablissez des capacités de\r\n  workflow de demande de service dans votre logiciel de support pour orchestrer\r\n  les escalades et les transferts<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Fournissez des capacités\r\n  d\'automatisation pour les requêtes utilisateurs courantes (accès,\r\n  réinitialisation du mot de passe, etc.)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Utilisez votre logiciel du\r\n  centre de services pour faciliter et enregistrer les communications entre les\r\n  agents et les demandeurs&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Intégrez vos systèmes du Centre\r\n  de services dans votre ITSM au sens plus large afin de fournir à vos agents\r\n  un accès plus étendu aux informations sur l\'environnement informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:aqua;mso-highlight:aqua\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:aqua;mso-highlight:\r\n  aqua\">La gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\n  Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Fournissez directement les\r\n  réponses aux questions fréquemment posées (FAQ) par les utilisateurs –\r\n  évitant ainsi le besoin de contacter un agent<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;\r\n  mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Types de logiciel qui supporte\r\n  le centre de services informatiques <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Un\r\n  centre de services informatiques efficace a besoin d\'une solide base technologique\r\n  pour fournir aux agents les outils et les informations permettant de répondre\r\n  efficacement aux besoins de demandeurs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Les\r\n  principaux :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\n  justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Système de tickets du support client<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le\r\n  système de tickets du support client est la plateforme transactionnelle clé\r\n  pour le centre de services informatique – orchestrant aussi bien les\r\n  incidents que les demandes de service dans toutes les fonctions du centre de\r\n  services et les équipes de support élargi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  background:darkblue;mso-highlight:darkblue\">Les <span style=\"color:white;\r\n  mso-themecolor:background1\">fonctions principales du système de tickets\r\n  comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:\r\n  darkblue\">• La gestion du workflow<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:\r\n  darkblue\">• Les alertes/escalades<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:\r\n  darkblue\">• Le routage automatique<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:\r\n  darkblue\">• La gestion des contrats/SLA</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n  color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\n  justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La connaissance\r\n  est la ressource la plus précieuse du centre de services et pour optimiser la\r\n  performance opérationnelle, il faut créer des données de la meilleure qualité\r\n  possible. Un système de gestion des connaissances est essentiel pour\r\n  canaliser cette ressource et s\'assurer que la connaissance organisationnelle\r\n  est disponible à ceux qui en ont besoin. Les fonctions principales d\'un\r\n  système de gestion des connaissances comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• <span style=\"background:lightgrey;mso-highlight:lightgrey\">Une base de données des\r\n  connaissances</span> (KMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• <span style=\"background:lightgrey;mso-highlight:lightgrey\">Les workflows de gestion\r\n  des connaissances</span> pour soutenir le cycle de vie des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Une base de\r\n  données des problèmes/ erreurs connues (KEDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Des vues\r\n  différentes des données pour les agents et les utilisateurs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Une recherche\r\n  par mots-clés évocateurs basés sur la description de l\'incident<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Libre-service pour l\'utilisateur final<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Les\r\n  capacités de support libre-service permettent aux utilisateurs de résoudre\r\n  leurs problèmes plus rapidement, sans avoir à attendre un agent. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Certaines\r\n  des fonctionnalités libre-service les plus courantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  La recherche dans la base de connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les diagnostics en libre-service<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les processus courants automatisés<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Le formulaire de demande de service<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\n  justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Gestion du centre de services et reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Les\r\n  fonctions de gestion et de reporting sont essentielles au sein du centre de\r\n  services lorsque les chefs de service cherchent à optimiser les coûts\r\n  opérationnels, identifier au préalable les problèmes impactant l\'entreprise\r\n  (incidents majeurs), gérer la satisfaction client et garantir le respect des\r\n  SLA. La technologie peut jouer un rôle important dans les fonctions de\r\n  gestion en permettant aux responsables du centre de services d\'avoir une vue\r\n  d\'ensemble de leurs opérations et des données nécessaires pour prendre des\r\n  décisions éclairées. Certaines des capacités principales de gestion et de\r\n  reporting du centre de services sont :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les capacités de gestion des <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">incidents</span>\r\n  majeurs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les tableaux de bord pour la <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">performance</span>\r\n  et la disponibilité des services<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">rapports</span> de\r\n  mesure sur les agents/la gestion des appels<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les rapports sur le respect des <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">SLA</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">analyses</span> des\r\n  problèmes connus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"986\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:369.7pt;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:698.3pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III.\r\n  La Gestion Des Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Définition<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ITSM signifie\r\n  Information Technology Service Management. L\'ITSM permet de voir son système\r\n  d\'information comme un service pour ses clients finaux et d\'en dégager une\r\n  valeur. Les logiciels d\'ITSM sont des logiciels informatiques conçus pour\r\n  gérer tous les services informatiques de l\'entreprise<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Pourquoi\r\n  mettre en place une gestion ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L\'implémentation\r\n  d\'une gestion ITSM efficace permet de fournir des services informatiques de\r\n  meilleure qualité à ses clients internes et externes, plus rapidement et avec\r\n  des coûts maitrisés. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ce\r\n  quoi un ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Aujourd’hui,\r\n  quelle que soit leur taille, les entreprises sont dépendantes de la\r\n  technologie et doivent d’une façon ou d’une autre interagir avec les services\r\n  informatiques. De plus en plus sollicités, ces services font face à des\r\n  problèmes récurrents : <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">manque\r\n  d’un management</span> et <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">d’une\r\n  visibilité globale des infrastructures</span>, <span style=\"background:yellow;\r\n  mso-highlight:yellow\">incidents mal qualifiés</span>, <span style=\"background:\r\n  yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">multitudes d’outils sans centralisation</span>, <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">gestion de multiples\r\n  configurations des outils,</span> etc. La complexité du rôle fait apparaître\r\n  des dysfonctionnements qui rendent les services peu efficients, augmentent\r\n  les coûts et dégradent la satisfaction.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L’un\r\n  des rôles clés de l’approche ITSM est d’aider les départements en charge des\r\n  infrastructures à simplifier leurs tâches en réduisant la complexité des\r\n  architectures informatiques et en unifiant les relations de travail entre\r\n  équipes informatiques et utilisateurs finaux.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Contexte\r\n  et bénéfice attendus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  Les entreprises sont de plus en plus dépendantes de leurs services\r\n  informatiques pour développer et maintenir un avantage concurrentiel sur leur\r\n  marché.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">•\r\n  L\'objectif du département informatique est de fournir, sous la pression les\r\n  services adaptés aux besoins <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:\r\n  yellow\">d\'aujourd\'hui</span> et d\'anticiper ceux de <span style=\"background:\r\n  yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">demain</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;\r\n  mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Intégration du CSI dans le ITSM<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le centre de\r\n  services informatiques fonctionne comme un élément des opérations de gestion\r\n  de service au sens large. Même si le centre de services informatiques peut\r\n  fonctionner de façon indépendante, la performance et la valeur seront\r\n  augmentées en intégrant le logiciel du centre de services avec d\'autres\r\n  parties du système ITSM de l\'entreprise. Certaines des intégrations les plus\r\n  intéressantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.\r\n  La base de données de la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2.\r\n  La gestion des changements<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3.\r\n  La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4.\r\n  La gestion des problèmes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">5.\r\n  La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La base de données de\r\n  la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Donnant aux\r\n  agents l’accès au réseau complexe des interdépendances techniques et aux\r\n  informations des composants de configuration pour leur permettre de mieux\r\n  évaluer les impacts des incidents<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des\r\n  changements<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Un grand nombre\r\n  de problèmes technologiques sont causés par des changements planifiés. En\r\n  donnant aux agents accès au système de gestion des changements, ils seront\r\n  capables d\'identifier les incidents associés plus rapidement<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Les\r\n  surveillants de service et d\'infrastructure donnent une visibilité en temps\r\n  réel sur la santé de l\'environnement informatique et donnent l’alerte lorsque\r\n  quelque chose ne va pas. En intégrant les capacités de surveillance avec le\r\n  système du centre de services, beaucoup d\'incidents peuvent être identifiés\r\n  sans que l’utilisateur n’ait besoin d\'appeler et de signaler un problème<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des\r\n  problèmes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Le meilleur\r\n  moyen de gérer les incidents est d\'éviter qu\'ils se produisent. Intégrer les\r\n  capacités de gestion des problèmes permet non seulement d\'aider les agents du\r\n  centre de services de comprendre quels problèmes connus sont déjà en train\r\n  d\'être traités, mais permet aussi aux équipes de gestion des problèmes de se\r\n  concentrer sur ceux qui causent le plus grand nombre d\'incidents.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">• Les\r\n  interactions du centre de services avec les utilisateurs sont un moment idéal\r\n  pour vérifier et mettre à jour les informations de gestion des actifs. Donner\r\n  aux agents la possibilité de voir et de mettre à jour les données de gestion\r\n  des actifs peut être un moyen efficace d\'améliorer la qualité de cet ensemble\r\n  de données importantes de l\'ITSM.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CONCLUSION<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le\r\n  centre de services informatiques est un élément essentiel de la fonction ITSM\r\n  des entreprises modernes. A mesure que le rôle de la technologie en tant que\r\n  partie intégrante des processus commerciaux et des expériences utilisateurs\r\n  s’élargit, il est essentiel de s\'assurer que les services technologiques\r\n  fonctionnent correctement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le\r\n  centre de services informatiques centré sur l\'utilisateur, avec ses workflows\r\n  bien définis, sa richesse de connaissances sur l\'organisation et ses\r\n  connexions avec le reste de l\'organisation informatique est le lien critique\r\n  entre les utilisateurs et l\'organisation informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chaque\r\n  organisation est unique et votre centre de services, ainsi que les outils que\r\n  vous utilisez, doivent être totalement en phase avec les besoins de votre\r\n  entreprise. Que votre organisation soit davantage centrée sur la technologie\r\n  et ait besoin d\'une solution ITSM intégrée, ou qu’elle ait une vue plus large\r\n  du centre de services en prenant en charge non seulement l’IT mais d\'autres\r\n  fonctions business qui utilisent un système de gestion du centre de services\r\n  clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>',	5,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	1),
(287,	108,	'BLABLABLA',	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; background: rgb(247, 202, 172);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">GESTION D’UN CENTRE INFORMATIQUE</span><u><o:p></o:p></u></span></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"1999\" style=\"width: 749.6pt; border: none;\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"1999\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 749.6pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Notion de centre informatique (CI)<o:p></o:p></span></u></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Définition</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un CI :</span></u></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> est un centre de traitement de données, un bureau ou un service responsable du traitement systématique des données et de l’information.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le traitement est effectué à l’aide d’ordinateurs équipés du matériel et des logiciels nécessaires pour accomplir cette tâche. Ces ordinateurs sont généralement mis en réseau et disposent d’une connexion Internet.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Mission</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un CI </span></u></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">est charge de la conception, l’implémentation et mais aussi la formation des utilisateurs, la maintenance du matériel informatique et le développement d’études de faisabilité font partie de ses missions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Centre informatique : où et quand<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Centre de dépouillement : il fonction comme un grand type de système informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les quatre activités principales de ce type de système:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">La saisie des données (saisie des données dans le système),<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le   stockage des données (généralement sur les serveurs),<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le traitement (somme des votes, estimation des pourcentages, et<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Sauvegarde des informations.</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Caractéristique (Etude préalable géographique)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> L’une des principales caractéristiques de ces établissements est la préservation des équipements au niveau physique. Tout d’abord :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#c45911;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Une localisation géographique</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> doit être choisie en tenant compte des différents points. Combien coute le terrain, le taxes, le redevance ou location, historique des catastrophes naturelles et la qualité de la communication…….<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> 2. <span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\">Gestion de température : </span>Climatiseur, ’orientation du bâtiment contre le rayon solaire…….<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 698.3pt;\"><td width=\"1013\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 379.9pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; height: 698.3pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">II. Le Centre De Service Informatique<o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Référencé Avec ITIL <span style=\"color: red;\">p9</span><o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Définition<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Le premier point de contact entre les utilisateurs et une organisation IT. <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u>Selon ITIL,</u></span> le centre de services est le point de contact unique (SPOC : Single Point of Contact) entre le prestataire de services (IT) et les utilisateurs pour les activités quotidiennes. Un centre classique gère les incidents et les demandes des services mais a traitant les communications des utilisateurs concernant les pannes ou les modifications dans le service. <span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\">Il couvre un large éventail et est pour fournir à l\'utilisateur un guichet unique pour tous leurs besoins informatiques. Ainsi, le centre de services joue<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Rôle : Faciliter l\'intégration des processus <span style=\"background: yellow;\">business</span> avec <span style=\"background: yellow;\">l\'écosystème technologique</span> et <span style=\"background: yellow;\">l\'infrastructure élargie de la gestion de services</span>.<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Origine et évolution dans la Gestion des Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La fonction du <span style=\"color: red;\">support client</span> est née à la fin des années 80 afin d’aider à régler les problèmes. Ils ne possédaient pas de SLA, ni d’objectifs basés sur le temps pour régler les problèmes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">ITIL est apparu dans les années 90, recensant les meilleures pratiques de la gestion des services informatiques, que le concept du centre de services informatiques centré sur l\'utilisateur a commencé à émerger.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Centre de Service informatique : Support Client et Centre d’Appel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le Support client :</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#385623;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:128\"=\"\"> </span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Est une ressource conçue pour fournir au client ou à l\'utilisateur interne des renseignements et du support associés aux processus, produits et services de l\'entreprise.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Canaux : Site physique, web, messagerie instantanées ou mail….<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le centre d’appel : </span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un centre d\'appels ou un centre de contacts est un point central qui gère les contacts et les<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Interactions clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(83, 129, 53);\">è<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"> </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";color:#538135;mso-themecolor:=\"\" accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Centre d\'appels</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";color:red\"=\"\"> </span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">entrants</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";color:red\"=\"\"> est comme le </span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";color:#538135;mso-themecolor:=\"\" accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">support produit.</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(83, 129, 53);\">è<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"> </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";color:#538135;mso-themecolor:=\"\" accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Les centres d\'appels sortants</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> sont utilisés pour des cas comme le télémarketing, le recouvrement de créances et les études de marché.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background: rgb(197, 224, 179);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Différenciation centrée sur ce que la fonction couvre et la façon dont ils sont structurés (CSI, CA et SC)<o:p></o:p></span></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"983\" style=\"width: 368.6pt; border: none;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 73.15pt;\"><td width=\"359\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 134.7pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; height: 73.15pt;\"><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm -5.35pt 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: center; line-height: 14.95px; background: rgb(247, 202, 172);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px;\">Centre de service informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Est stratégique car il participe à l’intégration des stratégies business pour créer de la valeur<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt -6.1pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p></td><td width=\"283\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 106.3pt; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; height: 73.15pt;\"><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm -5.35pt 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background: rgb(247, 202, 172);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Support Client<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Il est tactique car il permet de d’appliquer les stratégies qui ont été prise en compte par le CSI<o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=\"340\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 127.6pt; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; height: 73.15pt;\"><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm -5.35pt 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background: rgb(247, 202, 172);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Centre d’Appel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Gèrent les interactions, ont la portée la plus étendue en ce qui concerne les<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt -6.1pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Problèmes qu\'ils gèrent,<o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Rôles d’un Centre de Service Informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">-  Servir de premier point de contact pour la surveillance et la prise en charge des incidents en répondant aux demandes et aux questions des utilisateurs et en fournissant un canal de communication entre d\'autres fonctions de la gestion de services et la communauté des utilisateurs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">- Joue un rôle actif en ce qui concerne la capture des demandes de changement, la maintenance des contrats de support avec les parties tierces, la gestion des licences logicielles.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Que fait un centre de services informatiques ?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Dans certaines organisations, le centre de services est intégré à d\'autres processus business tels que :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> L’accueil des nouveaux employés<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> L’accueil et le départ des fournisseurs/partenaires<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> La gestion de l\'accès aux données<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> La surveillance de l\'infrastructure et des services<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> L’intégration des acquisitions<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Le reporting et la gestion des métriques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Avantages d\'un centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La <span style=\"background: red;\">réduction des coûts</span> et <span style=\"background: red;\">l’extensibilité</span> ;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Rester à <span style=\"background: red;\">l’écoute des utilisateurs</span> ;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:red;mso-highlight:red\"=\"\">Alerte précoce</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> des problèmes potentiels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les meilleures pratiques du centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les entreprises opèrent avec des centres de services informatiques depuis de nombreuses années, ce qui a permis d’identifier les meilleures pratiques.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:red;mso-highlight:red\"=\"\">L’engagement par rapport aux clients</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Analysez le comportement des clients et leurs attentes pour être sûr de comprendre leurs besoins.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez les SLA et les classifications de priorité/sévérité pour différentier les requêtes afin de gérer les plus urgentes en premier<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Essayez de résoudre les problèmes dès le premier point de contact et évitez les transferts, les escalades et les rappels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">2.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">La gestion du centre de services & le reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez les rapports en temps réel, les tableaux de bord et les statistiques du support client pour surveiller les opérations et lancer des actions de correction avant que les incidents ne deviennent des problèmes ;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Traitez le personnel du centre de services comme des professionnels de la communication et de la résolution de problèmes en leur donnant les outils dont ils ont besoin pour réussir<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">3.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:fuchsia;mso-highlight:fuchsia\"=\"\">Utiliser la technologie pour aider le centre de services informatiques</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Etablissez des capacités de workflow de demande de service dans votre logiciel de support pour orchestrer les escalades et les transferts<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Fournissez des capacités d\'automatisation pour les requêtes utilisateurs courantes (accès, réinitialisation du mot de passe, etc.)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez votre logiciel du centre de services pour faciliter et enregistrer les communications entre les agents et les demandeurs ;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Intégrez vos systèmes du Centre de services dans votre ITSM au sens plus large afin de fournir à vos agents un accès plus étendu aux informations sur l\'environnement informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:aqua;mso-highlight:aqua\"=\"\">4.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:aqua;mso-highlight:=\"\" aqua\"=\"\">La gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">  </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Fournissez directement les réponses aux questions fréquemment posées (FAQ) par les utilisateurs – évitant ainsi le besoin de contacter un agent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Types de logiciel qui supporte le centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un centre de services informatiques efficace a besoin d\'une solide base technologique pour fournir aux agents les outils et les informations permettant de répondre efficacement aux besoins de demandeurs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les principaux :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Système de tickets du support client<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le système de tickets du support client est la plateforme transactionnelle clé pour le centre de services informatique – orchestrant aussi bien les incidents que les demandes de service dans toutes les fonctions du centre de services et les équipes de support élargi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:darkblue;mso-highlight:darkblue\"=\"\">Les <span style=\"color: white;\">fonctions principales du système de tickets comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• La gestion du workflow<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• Les alertes/escalades<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• Le routage automatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• La gestion des contrats/SLA</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">2.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La connaissance est la ressource la plus précieuse du centre de services et pour optimiser la performance opérationnelle, il faut créer des données de la meilleure qualité possible. Un système de gestion des connaissances est essentiel pour canaliser cette ressource et s\'assurer que la connaissance organisationnelle est disponible à ceux qui en ont besoin. Les fonctions principales d\'un système de gestion des connaissances comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• <span style=\"background: lightgrey;\">Une base de données des connaissances</span> (KMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• <span style=\"background: lightgrey;\">Les workflows de gestion des connaissances</span> pour soutenir le cycle de vie des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Une base de données des problèmes/ erreurs connues (KEDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Des vues différentes des données pour les agents et les utilisateurs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Une recherche par mots-clés évocateurs basés sur la description de l\'incident<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">3.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Libre-service pour l\'utilisateur final<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les capacités de support libre-service permettent aux utilisateurs de résoudre leurs problèmes plus rapidement, sans avoir à attendre un agent.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Certaines des fonctionnalités libre-service les plus courantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• La recherche dans la base de connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les diagnostics en libre-service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les processus courants automatisés<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Le formulaire de demande de service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">4.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">      </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Gestion du centre de services et reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les fonctions de gestion et de reporting sont essentielles au sein du centre de services lorsque les chefs de service cherchent à optimiser les coûts opérationnels, identifier au préalable les problèmes impactant l\'entreprise (incidents majeurs), gérer la satisfaction client et garantir le respect des SLA. La technologie peut jouer un rôle important dans les fonctions de gestion en permettant aux responsables du centre de services d\'avoir une vue d\'ensemble de leurs opérations et des données nécessaires pour prendre des décisions éclairées. Certaines des capacités principales de gestion et de reporting du centre de services sont :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les capacités de gestion des <span style=\"background: lime;\">incidents</span> majeurs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les tableaux de bord pour la <span style=\"background: lime;\">performance</span> et la disponibilité des services<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les <span style=\"background: lime;\">rapports</span> de mesure sur les agents/la gestion des appels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les rapports sur le respect des <span style=\"background: lime;\">SLA</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les <span style=\"background: lime;\">analyses</span> des problèmes connus<o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=\"986\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 369.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; height: 698.3pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">III. La Gestion Des Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Définition<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">ITSM signifie Information Technology Service Management. L\'ITSM permet de voir son système d\'information comme un service pour ses clients finaux et d\'en dégager une valeur. Les logiciels d\'ITSM sont des logiciels informatiques conçus pour gérer tous les services informatiques de l\'entreprise<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Pourquoi mettre en place une gestion ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">L\'implémentation d\'une gestion ITSM efficace permet de fournir des services informatiques de meilleure qualité à ses clients internes et externes, plus rapidement et avec des coûts maitrisés.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Ce quoi un ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Aujourd’hui, quelle que soit leur taille, les entreprises sont dépendantes de la technologie et doivent d’une façon ou d’une autre interagir avec les services informatiques. De plus en plus sollicités, ces services font face à des problèmes récurrents : <span style=\"background: yellow;\">manque d’un management</span> et <span style=\"background: yellow;\">d’une visibilité globale des infrastructures</span>, <span style=\"background: yellow;\">incidents mal qualifiés</span>, <span style=\"background: yellow;\">multitudes d’outils sans centralisation</span>, <span style=\"background: yellow;\">gestion de multiples configurations des outils,</span> etc. La complexité du rôle fait apparaître des dysfonctionnements qui rendent les services peu efficients, augmentent les coûts et dégradent la satisfaction.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">L’un des rôles clés de l’approche ITSM est d’aider les départements en charge des infrastructures à simplifier leurs tâches en réduisant la complexité des architectures informatiques et en unifiant les relations de travail entre équipes informatiques et utilisateurs finaux.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Contexte et bénéfice attendus<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les entreprises sont de plus en plus dépendantes de leurs services informatiques pour développer et maintenir un avantage concurrentiel sur leur marché.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• L\'objectif du département informatique est de fournir, sous la pression les services adaptés aux besoins <span style=\"background: yellow;\">d\'aujourd\'hui</span> et d\'anticiper ceux de <span style=\"background: yellow;\">demain</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Intégration du CSI dans le ITSM<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le centre de services informatiques fonctionne comme un élément des opérations de gestion de service au sens large. Même si le centre de services informatiques peut fonctionner de façon indépendante, la performance et la valeur seront augmentées en intégrant le logiciel du centre de services avec d\'autres parties du système ITSM de l\'entreprise. Certaines des intégrations les plus intéressantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">1. La base de données de la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">2. La gestion des changements<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">3. La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">4. La gestion des problèmes<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">5. La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La base de données de la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Donnant aux agents l’accès au réseau complexe des interdépendances techniques et aux informations des composants de configuration pour leur permettre de mieux évaluer les impacts des incidents<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La gestion des changements<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Un grand nombre de problèmes technologiques sont causés par des changements planifiés. En donnant aux agents accès au système de gestion des changements, ils seront capables d\'identifier les incidents associés plus rapidement<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les surveillants de service et d\'infrastructure donnent une visibilité en temps réel sur la santé de l\'environnement informatique et donnent l’alerte lorsque quelque chose ne va pas. En intégrant les capacités de surveillance avec le système du centre de services, beaucoup d\'incidents peuvent être identifiés sans que l’utilisateur n’ait besoin d\'appeler et de signaler un problème<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La gestion des problèmes<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Le meilleur moyen de gérer les incidents est d\'éviter qu\'ils se produisent. Intégrer les capacités de gestion des problèmes permet non seulement d\'aider les agents du centre de services de comprendre quels problèmes connus sont déjà en train d\'être traités, mais permet aussi aux équipes de gestion des problèmes de se concentrer sur ceux qui causent le plus grand nombre d\'incidents.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les interactions du centre de services avec les utilisateurs sont un moment idéal pour vérifier et mettre à jour les informations de gestion des actifs. Donner aux agents la possibilité de voir et de mettre à jour les données de gestion des actifs peut être un moyen efficace d\'améliorer la qualité de cet ensemble de données importantes de l\'ITSM.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">CONCLUSION<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: yellow;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le centre de services informatiques est un élément essentiel de la fonction ITSM des entreprises modernes. A mesure que le rôle de la technologie en tant que partie intégrante des processus commerciaux et des expériences utilisateurs s’élargit, il est essentiel de s\'assurer que les services technologiques fonctionnent correctement.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: yellow;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le centre de services informatiques centré sur l\'utilisateur, avec ses workflows bien définis, sa richesse de connaissances sur l\'organisation et ses connexions avec le reste de l\'organisation informatique est le lien critique entre les utilisateurs et l\'organisation informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: yellow;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Chaque organisation est unique et votre centre de services, ainsi que les outils que vous utilisez, doivent être totalement en phase avec les besoins de votre entreprise. Que votre organisation soit davantage centrée sur la technologie et ait besoin d\'une solution ITSM intégrée, ou qu’elle ait une vue plus large du centre de services en prenant en charge non seulement l’IT mais d\'autres fonctions business qui utilisent un système de gestion du centre de services clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> </span></p>',	5,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	1);
INSERT INTO `crs_lecon` (`idLecon`, `idCours`, `titreLecon`, `lecon`, `idUtilisateur`, `dateCreation`, `actif`) VALUES
(288,	112,	'LECON ALGEBRE PARTIE3',	'<p><br></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Rôles d’un Centre de Service Informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">- &nbsp;Servir de premier point de contact pour la surveillance et la prise en charge des incidents en répondant aux demandes et aux questions des utilisateurs et en fournissant un canal de communication entre d\'autres fonctions de la gestion de services et la communauté des utilisateurs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">- Joue un rôle actif en ce qui concerne la capture des demandes de changement, la maintenance des contrats de support avec les parties tierces, la gestion des licences logicielles.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(217, 226, 243);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Que fait un centre de services informatiques ?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Dans certaines organisations, le centre de services est intégré à d\'autres processus business tels que :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;L’accueil des nouveaux employés<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;L’accueil et le départ des fournisseurs/partenaires<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;La gestion de l\'accès aux données<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;La surveillance de l\'infrastructure et des services<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;L’intégration des acquisitions<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;Le reporting et la gestion des métriques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Avantages d\'un centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La&nbsp;<span style=\"background: red;\">réduction des coûts</span>&nbsp;et&nbsp;<span style=\"background: red;\">l’extensibilité</span>&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Rester à&nbsp;<span style=\"background: red;\">l’écoute des utilisateurs</span>&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:red;mso-highlight:red\"=\"\">Alerte précoce</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;des problèmes potentiels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les meilleures pratiques du centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les entreprises opèrent avec des centres de services informatiques depuis de nombreuses années, ce qui a permis d’identifier les meilleures pratiques.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:red;mso-highlight:red\"=\"\">L’engagement par rapport aux clients</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Analysez le comportement des clients et leurs attentes pour être sûr de comprendre leurs besoins.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez les SLA et les classifications de priorité/sévérité pour différentier les requêtes afin de gérer les plus urgentes en premier<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Essayez de résoudre les problèmes dès le premier point de contact et évitez les transferts, les escalades et les rappels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">2.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">La gestion du centre de services &amp; le reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez les rapports en temps réel, les tableaux de bord et les statistiques du support client pour surveiller les opérations et lancer des actions de correction avant que les incidents ne deviennent des problèmes&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Traitez le personnel du centre de services comme des professionnels de la communication et de la résolution de problèmes en leur donnant les outils dont ils ont besoin pour réussir<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">3.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:fuchsia;mso-highlight:fuchsia\"=\"\">Utiliser la technologie pour aider le centre de services informatiques</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Etablissez des capacités de workflow de demande de service dans votre logiciel de support pour orchestrer les escalades et les transferts<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Fournissez des capacités d\'automatisation pour les requêtes utilisateurs courantes (accès, réinitialisation du mot de passe, etc.)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Utilisez votre logiciel du centre de services pour faciliter et enregistrer les communications entre les agents et les demandeurs&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Intégrez vos systèmes du Centre de services dans votre ITSM au sens plus large afin de fournir à vos agents un accès plus étendu aux informations sur l\'environnement informatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:aqua;mso-highlight:aqua\"=\"\">4.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:aqua;mso-highlight:=\"\" aqua\"=\"\">La gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Fournissez directement les réponses aux questions fréquemment posées (FAQ) par les utilisateurs – évitant ainsi le besoin de contacter un agent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Types de logiciel qui supporte le centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un centre de services informatiques efficace a besoin d\'une solide base technologique pour fournir aux agents les outils et les informations permettant de répondre efficacement aux besoins de demandeurs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les principaux :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Système de tickets du support client<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le système de tickets du support client est la plateforme transactionnelle clé pour le centre de services informatique – orchestrant aussi bien les incidents que les demandes de service dans toutes les fonctions du centre de services et les équipes de support élargi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:darkblue;mso-highlight:darkblue\"=\"\">Les&nbsp;<span style=\"color: white;\">fonctions principales du système de tickets comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• La gestion du workflow<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• Les alertes/escalades<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• Le routage automatique<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1;background:darkblue;mso-highlight:=\"\" darkblue\"=\"\">• La gestion des contrats/SLA</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">2.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Gestion des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La connaissance est la ressource la plus précieuse du centre de services et pour optimiser la performance opérationnelle, il faut créer des données de la meilleure qualité possible. Un système de gestion des connaissances est essentiel pour canaliser cette ressource et s\'assurer que la connaissance organisationnelle est disponible à ceux qui en ont besoin. Les fonctions principales d\'un système de gestion des connaissances comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">•&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lightgrey;\">Une base de données des connaissances</span>&nbsp;(KMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">•&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lightgrey;\">Les workflows de gestion des connaissances</span>&nbsp;pour soutenir le cycle de vie des connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Une base de données des problèmes/ erreurs connues (KEDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Des vues différentes des données pour les agents et les utilisateurs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Une recherche par mots-clés évocateurs basés sur la description de l\'incident<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-filename=\"R.png\" style=\"width: 934.133px; height: 467.066px;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">3.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Libre-service pour l\'utilisateur final<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les capacités de support libre-service permettent aux utilisateurs de résoudre leurs problèmes plus rapidement, sans avoir à attendre un agent.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Certaines des fonctionnalités libre-service les plus courantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• La recherche dans la base de connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les diagnostics en libre-service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les processus courants automatisés<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Le formulaire de demande de service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">4.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Gestion du centre de services et reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les fonctions de gestion et de reporting sont essentielles au sein du centre de services lorsque les chefs de service cherchent à optimiser les coûts opérationnels, identifier au préalable les problèmes impactant l\'entreprise (incidents majeurs), gérer la satisfaction client et garantir le respect des SLA. La technologie peut jouer un rôle important dans les fonctions de gestion en permettant aux responsables du centre de services d\'avoir une vue d\'ensemble de leurs opérations et des données nécessaires pour prendre des décisions éclairées. Certaines des capacités principales de gestion et de reporting du centre de services sont :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les capacités de gestion des&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">incidents</span>&nbsp;majeurs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les tableaux de bord pour la&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">performance</span>&nbsp;et la disponibilité des services<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">rapports</span>&nbsp;de mesure sur les agents/la gestion des appels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les rapports sur le respect des&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">SLA</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">• Les&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">analyses</span>&nbsp;des problèmes connus</span></p>',	5,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	1),
(289,	118,	'TSM',	'<h1 style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u>TSM</u></span>                                      </h1><h2 style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\"> Définition ITSM signifie Information Technology Service Management. L\'ITSM permet de voir son système d\'information comme un service pour ses clients finaux et d\'en dégager une valeur. Les logiciels d\'ITSM sont des logiciels informatiques conçus pour gérer tous les services informatiques</h2><h2 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 500;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 1.1;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" margin-top:=\"\" 20px;=\"\" margin-bottom:=\"\" 10px;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 30px;=\"\" font-style:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-caps:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" orphans:=\"\" 2;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" none;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" word-spacing:=\"\" -webkit-text-stroke-width:=\"\" text-decoration-thickness:=\"\" initial;=\"\" text-decoration-style:=\"\" text-decoration-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></h2><h2 style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"R (1).jpg\" class=\"note-float-left\" style=\"width: 544.836px; height: 272.418px; float: left;\">de l\'entreprise Pourquoi mettre en place une gestion ITSM ? L\'implémentation d\'une gestion ITSM efficace permet de fournir des services informatiques de meilleure qualité à ses clients internes et externes, plus rapidement et avec des coûts maitrisés. Ce quoi un ITSM ? Aujourd’hui, quelle que soit leur taille, les entreprises sont dépendantes de la technologie et doivent d’une façon ou d’une autre interagir avec les services informatiques. De plus en plus sollicités, ces services font face à des problèmes récurrents : manque d’un management et d’une visibilité globale des infrastructures, incidents mal qualifiés, multitudes d’outils sans centralisation, gestion de multiples configurations des outils, etc.<img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"OIP.jpg\" class=\"note-float-right\" style=\"width: 528.75px; height: 264.375px; float: right;\"> La complexité du rôle fait apparaître des dysfonctionnements qui rendent les services peu efficients, augmentent les coûts et dégradent la satisfaction. L’un des rôles clés de l’approche ITSM est d’aider les départements en charge des infrastructures à simplifier leurs tâches en réduisant la complexité des architectures informatiques et en unifiant les relations de travail entre équipes informatiques et utilisateurs finaux. Contexte et bénéfice attendus • Les entreprises sont de plus en plus dépendantes de leurs services informatiques pour développer et maintenir un avantage concurrentiel sur leur marché. • L\'objectif du département informatique est de fournir, sous la pression les services adaptés aux besoins d\'aujourd\'hui et d\'anticiper ceux de demain. Intégration du CSI dans le ITSM Le centre de services informatiques fonctionne comme un élément des opérations de gestion de service au sens large. Même si le centre de services informatiques peut fonctionner de façon indépendante, la performance et la valeur seront augmentées en intégrant le logiciel du centre de services avec d\'autres parties du système ITSM de l\'entreprise. Certaines des intégrations les plus intéressantes comprennent : 1. La base de données de la gestion de la configuration (CMDB) 2. La gestion des changements 3. La surveillance 4. La gestion des problèmes 5. La gestion des actifs</h2>',	5,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	1),
